---
Description: Apache Wedding Blessing
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 393
    Verse: 8
Tags:
  - Relationship
---
Now we will feel no rain for each of us will be shelter for the other. Now
we will feel no cold for each of us will be warmth for the other. Now there
will be no more loneliness for each of us will be companion to the other.
There is only one life before us and our seasons will be long and good.
